outage.title: Important Notice:
outage.description:
As of 6AM on Monday, February 18th, rising water levels on the Ohio River will force Harrah’s Metropolis to close. 

We will continue to monitor the water levels; however, the frequently changing river forecast makes it difficult to accurately determine the date and time we will reopen the hotel and casino. It is in the best interest and safety of our guests and employees that we remain closed until further notice.

As always, please check the Harrah’s Metropolis website, as well as our Facebook & Twitter pages for the most updated information.
